# Phase 1C — Schedule & Progress Tracker Implementation Plan

Phase 1A/1B delivered the foundation and reminder engine. Phase 1C now builds the **Schedule Management** and **Progress Tracker** features — daily agenda, event CRUD, course/project tracking with unit-level progress.

> [!NOTE]
> All new files follow established patterns: `@Inject`-based use cases, `@HiltViewModel` ViewModels with `StateFlow` + `SharedFlow<UiEvent>`, and dark-themed Compose screens using the existing `Color.kt` palette. No new Gradle dependencies are needed.

