## Verification Plan

### Automated/Local Tests
- Verify the project compiles with all new files via Android Studio build

### Manual Verification (Real Device)
- Create a schedule event → verify it appears in the daily agenda
- Switch dates → verify the date selector correctly filters events
- Delete an event → verify removal from list
- Create a course tracker with 3 modules → verify progress bar shows 0%
- Complete 1 module → verify progress bar updates to ~33%, `currentUnitLabel` changes
- Complete all modules → verify tracker shows 100% and `completedAt` is set
- Create a project tracker → verify it shows under "Projects" filter
- Navigate: List → Create → Detail → back, verify smooth transitions
